title: No. 23 Virginia Tech battles back, falls 68-66 to No. 3 NC State - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 23 Virginia Tech battles back, falls 68-66 to No. 3 NC State  VT hokiesports.com
description: BLACKSBURG, VA --The Virginia Tech offense put on a ball-movement clinic at home Sunday, collecting 14 assists on 23 made shots, but the Hokies fell to the NC State Wolfpack 68-66.
